N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 800.6 - Berthing of vessels

State Regulations

Berthing space to be occupied by vessels utilizing the
commission facilities, shall be designated and assigned by the person
authorized by the commission. Notes
